      <p xml:id="" begin="01:02:19.150" end="01:02:21.360"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">Comme tout le monde à</span> 
<span tts:fontStyle="italic">Toritama,</span></p>
      <p xml:id="" begin="01:02:21.860" end="01:02:25.270"><span tts:fontStyle="italic">Léo veut passer le Carnaval</span>
